**/*.md
# …but project-app catalog content under store/projects/ ships REAL markdown at
# runtime — agent definitions (spaces/*/agents/*/{charter,instruct}.md) and
# knowledge (*.md). Excluding them made the store build a manifest without any
# agents, so installed apps' <Chat> failed "agent not found". Re-include them.
!store/projects/**/*.md
sdk/org/docs/
